  "description": "Thor, the mighty god of thunder, lightning, and storms, stands as the foremost champion of the Aesir against the forces of chaos. Son of Odin and the earth goddess Jord, Thor wields Mjolnir, the hammer that never misses and always returns to his hand. His belt Megingjord doubles his already immense strength, and his iron gloves Jarngreipr allow him to wield the hammer. Thor travels in a chariot drawn by the goats Tanngrisnir and Tanngnjostr, which he can eat and resurrect daily. Red-bearded and quick to anger, he is humanity's defender against the frost giants of Jotunheim. At Ragnarok, Thor will slay the World Serpent Jormungandr but fall to its venom.",
